61#define PJ_DECL_LIST_MEMBER(type) \
62 \
63 type *prev; \
64 \
65 type *next
66
67
73struct pj_list
74{
75 PJ_DECL_LIST_MEMBER(void);
76} PJ_ATTR_MAY_ALIAS; /* may_alias avoids warning with gcc-4.4 -Wall -O2 */

87PJ_INLINE(void) pj_list_init(pj_list_type * node)
88{
89 ((pj_list*)node)->next = ((pj_list*)node)->prev = node;
90}
91
92
101PJ_INLINE(int) pj_list_empty(const pj_list_type * node)
102{
103 return ((pj_list*)node)->next == node;
104}
